Author: GitHub
Title: Come with me to my first GitHub Universe!
Description:
Come with me to my very first GitHub Universe! After spending so much time connecting with the community online, I'm finally getting to experience the "world's fair of software" in person. I can't wait to meet the people behind the code and capture the energy of this unique event.
